pos review: Excellent breakfast. Great location, 15 minute walk to station or town centre. Friendly staff.
neg review: The absence of tea/coffee making facilities in room. The communal tea/coffee facility was out of order a couple of times.

pos review: very close to the center, sweet nice room
friendly clean and local would reccomend.
Very nice hotel, in a quiet area, parking place available, clean, nice staff. The room was clean, large bathroom, nice backyard, plenty of chairs and tables to enjoy a warm evening with the friends.
Great location and very friendly staff. Good we could use the hotel car park
neg review: Would have been good to know the car park was not included in the price quoted on booking.com

pos review: Very convenient to the Square and and ideal place for us as we had 8 motorbikes which were parked overnight in secure parking as long as you reserve,friendly staff and comfortable rooms highly recommended
A beautiful hotel, perfect for what we wanted, perfectly situated with very friendly staff.
